# AI-Powered Credit Card Fraud Detection

## Project Overview
This project uses Machine Learning to detect fraudulent credit card transactions. It includes data preprocessing, exploratory data analysis (EDA), model training, evaluation, and an interactive Streamlit dashboard.

## Features
- Fraud Detection using Random Forest
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Interactive Streamlit Dashboard
- ROC Curve Visualization
- Confusion Matrix
- Feature Importance Analysis
- Fraud Transaction Insights

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-Learn
- Plotly
- Streamlit

## Model Performance
- Random Forest Classifier
- ROC-AUC Analysis
- Precision, Recall, and F1-Score Evaluation

## Dashboard Screenshots
- Dashboard Overview
- Confusion Matrix
- ROC Curve
- Feature Importance

## Live Demo
https://ai-fraud-detection-bdddpqjaimhycymudy79bt.streamlit.app/

